turns.text: I have the Muse available for 12 days but that is only a 2 star hotel. However, I do have some suggestions. I have some excellent options available during that time period. A nice 4 star hotel in Calgary, Canada, another nice 4 star hotel in Marseille or a 4.5 star hotel in Frankfurt, Germany all with direct flights from Portland. Do any of these cities interest you?
The Marseille and Germany packages are very attractive. I'd like to know more about hotel in the Marseille package. Is breakfast included?

The Hotel Duchesse in Marseille is a 4 star hotel which provides you with free wifi, but breakfast is not included in the price. It is available from Sunday August 21st to Sunday August 28th. I forgot to ask, will you be travelling alone or with a companion?
I will be travelling alone. How much is this package?
This package on an economy flight is worth a total of $3049.54USD. Are you interested in booking it?
I am, but first I'd like to see what the price is with an upgrade to business class, and perhaps compare this package to the Germany deal.

There are no longer business class seats available for this particular package to Marseille. The Mellow Palms Resort in Frankfurt is a 10 day package available from Aug 19 to Aug 27 and includes free wifi and free breakfast and has a 4.5 star rating. The total cost on this package, also based on an economy class flight is $3091.3USD.
Is it possible to upgrade the Frankfurt flight to business class?
This package is also only available with an economy class seat.
That's fine. I will book the 10 day Germany Mellow Palms Resort vacation package.
I will get that all booked up for you and send you an email confirmation.
Great, thank you. I will most certainly book my next vacation with you.
Enjoy your trip!
Hi im planning my Spring break can you help me find the best deals?
Of course! How many people will you be traveling with?

n_adults.value: my three best friends and myself

we are in Montreal

Great, I'd like to book this one please.
Sure thing, consider it done!

Hi, I need to go to Mos Eisley for a wedding, leaving on Saturday, August 13, 2016 and returning on Tuesday, August 16, 2016. Preferably for $3700.
Would you like to have a departure from a specific location?

For sure! How many of you will be travelling together?
me and my 3 best friends!
And where will you be departing from?
we want to leave on the 16th were looking to go to San Juan
Okay, but where from? From what city?
We're leaving from Godric's Hollow
I have no flights leaving out of Godric's Hollow. If you are able to leave from Cleveland or Montreal, then I can send you to San Juan.
we could leave from birmingham do you have anything from there?
to San Juan?
if possible
I have no flights to San Juan from Birmingham Are there any other places that you would like to travel to? I have packages to Japan from Birmingham.
what are the ones to japan like do they fit my budget?
I do not know what your budget is. Can you please tell me?
I am sorry, I made a mistake, I do not have direct flights from Birmingham to Japan either.
honestly it seems like nothing will work here! thanks!
Sorry I wish I could have been of more help to you. Next time!
Hi wozbot! I'd like to book a spring break vacation for myself and 3 of my best friends
Hello, from where would you like to leave? Do you have an idea of where you would like to go?
We'll be leaving from Goiania. Rosario is the place to be this year! Our spring break starts on August 28 and ends on September 4, can you find us something between those dates?

turns.text: I have several flights leaving on the 8th or the 12th of September.
when would they be returning?
If you would like to fly out on the 8th you will be returning on the 14th. If you would like to fly out on the 12th you will be returning on the 18th.
can we book the one that returns on the 18th?

Actually I have several packages returning on the 18th. You can choose between a business and an economy flight and two hotels: The Sunny Wolf Inn & Suites, a 2.5-star hotel which has a 8.22/10 guest rating, or the Majestic Mountain Inn a 2.5-star hotel which has a which has a 6.91/10 guest rating. Both hotels include free parking, free wifi and free breakfast.
the sunny wolf seems to be a better place. how much would that be?
With an economy flight your total comes to 706.97USD. With a business flight your total comes to 795.22USD.
can we book the economy flight?
Absolutely, your trip has been booked!
Thank you! Goodbye.
Hello wozbot!
Hey there! How can I help you?
My husband and I are recently married, we are looking for a honeymoon vacation.
Where were you thinking?
Perhaps Toronto. We are currently in Rome for business, we'd like to leave from here. We're looking at going from August 18 to August 29th.

I have departures available on September 1st, September 7th and September 8th. I have two choices in hotels - the Vertex Inn or the Winter Hill Inn., both of which are rated two stars.

Availability is from Sept 1st to the 9th, Sept 7 to the 15th and Sept 8th to the 16th. I do not have any hotels available with a better rating. Please do note that both hotels have free parking, free breakfast and free wifi. Are you looking for a flight in economy class or business class?

In economy or business class?
for business class
For business class at the Vertex Inn in San Antonio Sept 7 to Sept 15th, the price is $1477.34.
in contrast to mannheim?

Also in business class in San Antonio, I have the Winter Hill either from Sept 1st to 9th or Sept 8th to the 16th at $1477.00. Business class to the Regal in Mannheim is $3451.00 if you choose to go Aug 27 to Aug 31st and if you pick the week of Sept 6th to the 10th, it is $4249.00.

Okay I will get all your information and we will proceed with the booking. We appreciate your business.
thank you very much
